{"tid":2116273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2003年沙士疫潮","createTime":"2020-07-20T05:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T05:34:34.000Z","uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35a81a9963a19b1ce787f00105b547f8e8d248d9","tid":2116273,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:11:18.000Z","msg":"2003年沙士疫潮」是指香港在2003年2月至6月期間爆發嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症（Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome，香港將簡稱SARS音譯為「沙士」，未命名時稱「非典型肺炎」），造成共1755人染病，299人死亡，是香港近年最嚴重的瘟疫，亦對香港的政治、經濟、社會各個方面影響深遠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人離死亡不遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef26c48618251a89149442a43d6305428bd92c70","tid":2116273,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade79fd80c339423ed138e46d319c521694233ba","tid":2116273,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"武肺死亡率低好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522474b94e632482936ed011dbbd4e308fa29a3a","tid":2116273,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ade79fd80c339423ed138e46d319c521694233ba","tid":2116273,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"武肺死亡率低好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:14:32.000Z","msg":"睇外國數指<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601cb1d9361e3c58aefc18d4da56f3fedc38e769","tid":2116273,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543c97b9e7cbf16d1b571714e40cdadbfc6457e3","tid":2116273,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ade79fd80c339423ed138e46d319c521694233ba","tid":2116273,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"武肺死亡率低好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:34:34.000Z","msg":"感染多但人死得越少，後果係最嚴重，好似沙士康復者，大多受骨腐影響。武漢肺炎康復者，就受肺功能影響。人數越多以後醫療體整一大負擔"}]}